{"word":"G2018 - ἐπιφέρω - epiphérō - ep-ee-fer'-o - Add","slug":"G2018","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epiphérō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-fer'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Add"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03C6;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9; - epiphero&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ee-fer'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>; to <i>bear upon</i> (or <i>further</i>), that is, <i>adduce</i> (personally or judicially [<i>accuse</i>, <i>inflict</i>]), <i>superinduce:</i> - add, bring (against), take."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414\">G5414</a>"}]}